flowchart LR
  Source[SOP source text] --> OP[OP record]
  OP --> Edge[Operation hyperedge]
  Edge --> Req[Requirement]
  Req --> Review[Expert review]
  Review -->|confirm| Confirmed[Confirmed requirement]
  Review -->|reject| Rejected[Rejected requirement]
  Review -->|clarify| Clarification[Clarification]
  Clarification --> Source
  Req --> Evidence[sourceOps and sourceHyperedges]
  Evidence --> OP
  Evidence --> Edge

